        "speaker": "Lenny Rachitsky",
        "timestamp": "00:17:45",
        "quote": "I know another element of this that is really important to you that you have shifted the way you all operate is focusing on impact. There was a lot of focus on just building a lot of stuff and you realize there's a lot of power in thinking from perspective of how do we have the most impact? Talk about that.",
