        "timestamp": "00:27:43",
        "quote": "Yeah. And I think another thing for me, it's an exercise that I really encourage everyone to do. For me, it was after the columns hackathon and everything that we talked about, I said, \"Okay, each quarter...\" and this is when we were much smaller, but it can be each month, it can be each two weeks, but how do I imagine the company and the product is going to be different and better for our customers in a quarter from now? And from that, walk it backwards.",
